<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA14">
<l>tāṉē taṉineñcan taṉṉaiyuyak koḷvāṉ</l>
<l>ṟāṉē peruñcēmañ ceyyumā - ṟāṉēyōr</l>
<l>pūṇākat tāṟpolintu poṅkaḻalcēr nañcumiḻu</l>
<l>nīṇākat tāṉai niṉaintu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Itself, in order to take itself to escaping my solitary heart</l>
<l>has indeed made itself a great shelter – thinking of</l>
<l>him with the long snake that spit up the poison joined by churning fire,</l>
<l>flourishing as a unique ornament on [his] chest.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
